videos.headline: Ridder connects with Whyle for Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Cincinnati takes a 7-0 lead over SMU as Desmond Ridder completes a pass to Josh Whyle to score a seven-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder connects with Whyle for Cincinnati TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder navigates his way to 15-yard Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder keeps it as he forces his way through SMU defenders and up the sideline to score a 15-yard touchdown and extend Cincinnati's lead to 14-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder navigates his way to 15-yard Cincinnati TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rice makes the grab to score SMU's first TD
videos.description: With the defense trailing him, Rashee Rice reaches out to make the tumbling grab to score a nine-yard SMU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rice makes the grab to score SMU's first TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder burns SMU for 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder turns on the jets as he dodges SMU defenders, leaving them in the dust as he reaches the end zone for a 32-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder burns SMU for 2nd rushing TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder breaks out for 91-yard TD run
videos.description: Desmond Ridder takes off to score a 91-yard touchdown, his third of the day, to push the Cincinnati lead to 35-13 over SMU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder breaks out for 91-yard TD run) 2020/10/24 ESHEET
